    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>The Bone-Singer is a towering skeletal form wrapped in chains of bone and ancient cloth — a large undead conjurer whose voice resonates like wind through a tomb, beautiful and deeply wrong. It commands the barrow-draugr through song, raising new minions from the earth with its Arise ability and draining life from the living with Drain Life. When its Hit Points drops dangerously low, its Choir of Death unleashes a devastating psychic scream. Its Dread Aura suppresses the will of all living creatures nearby.</p>",
